text: Podkovák is a nature reserve in the Český les Protected Landscape Area. This landscape area is in the western part of the Plzeň Region of the Czech Republic. It covers a small bog forest in a depression. It has Pinus uncinata ssp. rotundata trees. Wood grouses are seen in the area.
